sequenceDiagram
    actor Chef
    participant ChefApp as chef-admin
    participant Engine as OrderOrchestrator
    participant Kitchen as KitchenEngine
    participant DB as Supabase

    Note over DB: Order status = submitted
    DB-->>ChefApp: Realtime notification (new order)

    Chef->>ChefApp: View new orders dashboard
    ChefApp->>DB: GET orders (status=submitted, storefront_id)
    DB-->>ChefApp: list of pending orders

    Chef->>ChefApp: Open order detail
    ChefApp->>DB: GET order + order_items + customer info
    DB-->>ChefApp: order detail

    Chef->>ChefApp: Accept order (estimated prep = 25 min)
    ChefApp->>Engine: acceptOrder(orderId, estimatedMinutes=25)

    Engine->>DB: UPDATE orders (status=accepted, accepted_at=now())
    Engine->>DB: INSERT order_status_history (accepted)
    Engine->>Kitchen: updateQueue(orderId, status=accepted, eta=25)
    Kitchen->>DB: UPDATE kitchen_queue_entries (estimated_mins=25)
    Engine->>DB: INSERT notifications (customer, type=order_accepted)
    Engine->>DB: INSERT sla_timers (stage=prep, target=1500s)
    Engine-->>ChefApp: { status: "accepted" }

    Chef->>ChefApp: Start preparing
    ChefApp->>Engine: startPreparing(orderId)

    Engine->>DB: UPDATE orders (status=preparing)
    Engine->>DB: INSERT order_status_history (preparing)
    Engine->>Kitchen: updateQueue(orderId, status=in_progress, started_at=now())
    Kitchen->>DB: UPDATE kitchen_queue_entries (status=in_progress, started_at)
    Engine-->>ChefApp: { status: "preparing" }

    Chef->>ChefApp: Mark as ready for pickup
    ChefApp->>Engine: markReady(orderId)

    Engine->>DB: UPDATE orders (status=ready, ready_at=now())
    Engine->>DB: INSERT order_status_history (ready)
    Engine->>Kitchen: completeQueue(orderId)
    Kitchen->>DB: UPDATE kitchen_queue_entries (status=completed, completed_at)
    Engine->>DB: INSERT notifications (driver dispatcher)
    Engine-->>ChefApp: { status: "ready" }

    Note over Engine: Triggers DispatchEngine.createDelivery()
